Class TermVector<T extends Term>

  • java.lang.Object
    • nars.term.TermVector<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable, java.lang.Iterable<T>, TermContainer<T>, Termlike
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    EllipsisMatch, TermSet

    public class TermVector<T extends Term>
extends java.lang.Object
implements TermContainer<T>, java.io.Serializable
    Holds a vector or tuple of terms. Useful for storing a fixed number of subterms TODO make this class immutable and term field private provide a MutableTermVector that holds any write/change methods
